@startuml DocCheck_Sequence
title DocCheck Module - Assessment Flow Sequence

actor Seller
participant Frontend
participant DocCheckAPI
participant Database
participant NotificationService

Seller -> Frontend: Access /verificar (DocCheck tool)
Frontend -> Frontend: Load assessment form
Frontend -> Seller: Display Question 1

loop For Each of 8 Questions
  Seller -> Frontend: Answer question
  Frontend -> Frontend: Update local state
  Frontend -> Seller: Display next question
end

Seller -> Frontend: Complete all 8 answers
Frontend -> Frontend: Show email capture form
Seller -> Frontend: Enter email address
Frontend -> DocCheckAPI: POST /doccheck/evaluate {answers}

DocCheckAPI -> DocCheckAPI: Evaluate document matrix
DocCheckAPI -> DocCheckAPI: Determine service tier
DocCheckAPI -> DocCheckAPI: Calculate price & timeline
DocCheckAPI -> DocCheckAPI: Identify risk flags

DocCheckAPI --> Frontend: Return DocCheckResult
Frontend -> Database: Save DocCheckSession
Database --> Frontend: Session saved

Frontend -> Seller: Display result page
Seller -> Seller: Review documents & tier recommendation

alt Convert to Order
  Seller -> Frontend: Click "Encomendar"
  Frontend -> Database: Update session.converted = true
  Database --> Frontend: Confirmation
  Frontend -> Seller: Redirect to /encomendar
else No Conversion
  Seller -> Frontend: Close assessment
  Frontend -> NotificationService: Send follow-up email
  NotificationService --> Seller: Email sent (24h later)
end

note right of DocCheckAPI
  Decision tree evaluation
  Conditional document logic
  Price calculation with discounts
end note

@enduml
